	    </pre></td></tr></table></td></tr></table></td><td bgcolor="#999999"><img src="source-id:5:xhtml:html/en/images/empty.png" width="1" height="1" /></td></tr><tr><td bgcolor="#555555"><img src="source-id:5:xhtml:html/en/images/empty.png" width="1" height="1" /></td><td bgcolor="#555555"><img src="source-id:5:xhtml:html/en/images/empty.png" width="1" height="1" /></td><td bgcolor="#555555"><img src="source-id:5:xhtml:html/en/images/empty.png" width="1" height="1" /></td></tr></table></td></tr></table></pre>
	    
	    <pre>tar -xzf icu-2.8.tgz
cd icu/source
chmod +x runConfigureICU configure install-sh
./runConfigureICU --disable-64bit-libs
make &amp;&amp; make install</pre>
	 </li>
      </ul>
      <p>If you have any difficulties installing ICU, refer to <a href="http://oss.software.ibm.com/cvs/icu/~checkout~/icu/readme.html?tag=release-2-8">icu/readme.html</a>.</p>

